{"tid":1680825,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[重溫初心]譴責林鄭，對抗警暴","createTime":"2019-10-29T05:00:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T06:07:27.000Z","uid":5202,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"940fe66184a0a24c87c29dcc757952b6c79e4480","tid":1680825,"uid":5202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T05:00:01.000Z","msg":"運動進展至今已經三個月，禁蒙面法出台起，「五大訴求，缺一不可」的聲音已漸見微弱。本來最該被讉責的特首，在警暴加持下安然推警察為她的代罪羔羊，不斷安然出現在大家視線內。<br />\n作為一個連登CD Rom，我忍不住想問問大家，點解始作俑者林鄭現時可以置身事外，對市民與警察之間的衝突冷眼旁觀？<br />\n我的看法是，現時我們所做的一切，除了針對中資、藍底及警暴外，是否應該幫林鄭回到鎂光燈下，接受市民及國際社會的注目禮？<br />\n<br />\n認同請幫手推post，否則就由佢沉吧"},{"pid":"c6a03014d7b7eca9a9042520788a13858b2e28d2","tid":1680825,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T05:00:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jc8536k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJc8536k.jpg&h=6d7fb408&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"15dace2d3499bc7795e1dd9eb88f858f4864e9de","tid":1680825,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T06:07:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qEwvxin.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqEwvxin.png&h=699b7c9c&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}